Interface SelectUsecase.Creator

  • Enclosing class:
    SelectUsecase

    private static interface SelectUsecase.Creator
    This enumeration is created to simplify the different use cases. Login: a user logs in to the system. RegisterPatient: The nurse logs the new patient in to the system. Nothing: Returns immediatly to the select usecase. Logout: a user can log out from the system. Exit System: The system will be closed.
